programme.title: Citra: Aku Yang Kau Tinggalkan Ep1
programme.desc: Majlis perkahwinan Ani bersama cucu Puan Zainun semakin hampir. Ani yang sebelum ini setuju untuk dikahwinkan mula meragui keputusannya. Nia terkejut dengan pengakuan Ani tentang hubungannya bersama Sazali. Nia dan Zaril Ikhwan berkahwin bukan kerana cinta. Nia memerlukan wang untuk membantu keluarganya, Zaril Ikhwan pula pembantu menjaga dirinya yang sakit. Dalam diam Nia jatuh cinta kepada suaminya. Namun, akibat salah faham, Nia telah disingkirkan. Nia meninggalkan Zaril Ikhwan dan membawa hati ke Turin meneruskan hidupnya disana. Takdir menentukan mereka bertemu semula di Turin, Italy. Walaupun masih ada dendam dan rahsia yang dipendam, demi untuk meneruskan hidup ini, perpisahan secara rasmi adalah jalan yang terbaik buat mereka berdua. Namun Nia dan Zaril Ikhwan merasakan diri masing-masing yang sebenarnya telah ditinggalkan. Apakah rahsia yang dipendamkan itu? Pelakon: Ungku Ismail Aziz, Elizad Sharifuddin, Natasya Mahyan, Adam Shadan, Aedy Ashraf, Husna Mustaffa, Roy Azman, Laila Nasir, dan Safwan Nazri.

programme.title: Spektra: Kau? C.E.O Aku? Ep18
programme.desc: Aisya berkahwin dengan Danial atas pilihan keluarga, namun perkahwinan mereka terganggu akibat kehadiran Mila, teman rapat Danial. Setelah kehilangan anak, Danial memutuskan untuk berkahwin dengan Mila, sementara Aisya terpaksa menerima keputusan itu. Namun, Aisya mendapat sokongan teman-temannya, Anis, Syafiq, dan Hakimi, yang berusaha memperjuangkan haknya. Dalam episod ini ibu Aisya, Hajah Marina curiga dengan Mila setelah melihat Aisya trauma melihat Mila. Aisya telah memberitahu Anis apa yang berlaku. Anis mahu membuat laporan polis tapi dihalang Aisya kerana tiada bukti dan akan membahayakan nyawa orang lain. Danial menghantar Aisya berpantang di kampungnya. Aisya meminta Danial melupakan hal yang telah berlaku dan memulakan hidup baru. Pelakon: Azrel Ismail, Puteri Aishah, Syazwan Zulkifly, Neera Azizi, Talha Harith, Siti Hariesa, Trisha Ooi, Zuhairi Ibrahim, Anne Abdullah, Amelina, Ainina Ahmad, dan Zalfa Zin

programme.title: Kembara Backpackers Bersama Moji (Siri 2) Ep8
programme.desc: Sebuah majalah travelog yang mengikuti pengembaraan Moji menjelajah dunia secara backpacking. Dalam siri kali ini, Moji meneroka keindahan dan cabaran di sepanjang laluan ikonik Trans-Siberian. Episod kali ini, Moji memulakan pengembaraan ke Tasik Baikal, Siberia Russia. programme.desc: Dalam rancangan ini Cef Fendi dan Ustaz Hakim akan meninjau ke ladang nanas di Pontian Johor dan akan memasak masakan yang berasaskan dari buah nanas. Menu yang akan dimasak dalam episod kali ini ialah Makanan Laut Masam Manis, Nasi Goreng Nanas, dan Nanas Bakar Kulit Kayu Manis.

programme.title: Di Sisimu Aku Ep6
programme.desc: Qeena menatap gambar Mad dan Rohani. Rasa sedih dan rindu. Lama tidak tahu khabar kedua orang tua yang banyak berjasa kepadanya. Qeena tidak bertanya pun tentang ma, abah, adik-adik kpd Aman. Lupa mahu bertanya sebab sedih. Rasa takut pun ada. Aman pula menyindir Qeena yang diam terus. Qeena tidak menafikan mahupun iyakan. Cerita lama terlalu sedih.

programme.title: 25 Nabi Ep8
programme.desc: Episod kali ini menceritakan mengenai kisah Nabi Luth a.s . Penceritaan akan bermula dari pendahuluan sehinggalah kisah-kisah yang berkaitan dengan peristiwa yang membawa kepada contoh dan teladan bagi umat Islam.

programme.title: Pengantin 3 Hari
programme.desc: Tamat sahaja belajar di universiti, Maya buat keputusan untuk membantu emaknya ubah nasib keluarga. Maya akhirnya setuju untuk bekerja dengan Zura setelah dipujuk beberapa kali. Pada hari pertama, Maya mula pelik apabila dia dibawa menyelusuri sebuah lorong untuk pergi ke tempat kerja Zura. Rupa-rupanya Maya diperdaya Zura. Zura hidup mewah dengan pekerjaan yang tak bermaruah sebagai ibu ayam kepada gadis-gadis polos seperti Maya. Perkenalan singkat Maya dan Ikram membawa mereka ke jinjang pelamin. Selepas tiga hari bergelar isteri, Maya diceraikan. Hanya air mata yang membasahi pipi.

programme.title: Puji Pujian & Kalam AllahV1

programme.title: Salam Nusantara Pulau Jawa Ep8
programme.desc: Garut yang terletak di pedalaman Jawa Barat sangat terkenal dengan perusahaan dodol dan industri yang berasaskan kulit. Selain itu, perniagaan anyaman tikar mahupun bakul dan juga sendel juga terkenal dan tidak lupa juga perniagaan trompa yang mampu merawat sakit-sakit dalaman seperti migrane, sakit pinggang dan lain. Walaupun perniagaan-perniagaan di kampung-kampung pedalaman ini tampak mudah namun ianya adalah sumber utama dalam ekonomi di Bandung.

programme.title: Religious Clip S96 Ep3

programme.title: Setia Menunggumu Ep13
programme.desc: Rahman masih terkejut, dia memberitahu bahawa Adi adalah anaknya dengan bukti dokumen yang ditunjukkan oleh Adi itu. Lalu Rahman membawa Adi berjumpa dengan Zainab (mak kandung Adi). Mereka menyuruh Adi tinggal bersama dengan mereka, tetapi Adi memilih untuk tinggal di madrasah sahaja. Sekali sekala Zainab menyuruh Sakinah menjemput Adi untuk datang ke rumah mereka, Rahman dan Zainab mahu memberikan apa sahaja untuk Adi kerana dia telah meninggalkan Adi hampir 20 tahun. Zainab dan Rahman mahu jodohkan Adi dengan Sakinah.

programme.title: Kebesaran Hati Seorang Ayah Melindungi Anak Tiri Yang Dibesarkannya
programme.desc: Pak Galih terkejut ketika melihat Tia, iaitu wanita yang ingin dikahwini Anto. Tia merupakan bekas isteri Pak Galih dan pernah mengandungkan Dela. Tia yang cuba mengikis harta Pak Galih dan kini dia hendak mengikis harta Anto. Semuanya terbongkar apabila Anto mendengar perbulan Tia dengan Pak Galih. Tia dimasukkan ke hospital mental kerana hendak membunugh diri namun akhirnya meninggal dunia.

programme.desc: Rasya Aleeya dan Syed Reeza mula berkenalan melalui SMS, membina hubungan cinta walaupun Rasya mengalami paranoia dan Reeza dikenali sebagai lelaki yang suka menggoda. Hubungan mereka diuji apabila Rasya sukar mempercayai Reeza, dipengaruhi masa lalunya dan hasutan Adri, rakan Reeza. Namun, perasaan mereka berdua kembali bercambah selepas bertemu semula di Dubai. Rasya berasa bersalah atas kesilapan lalu tetapi akhirnya mereka berjaya mengatasi salah faham dan ketakutan yang menghalang cinta mereka. Rancangan Reeza untuk menguji perasaan Rasya berjaya memecahkan ego dan ketakutannya. Mereka akhirnya berkahwin dan mendapat restu keluarga, membuktikan cinta sejati mereka mampu bertahan walaupun diuji pelbagai cabaran.

programme.title: 11 Cinta Sebelum Kamu
programme.desc: Ray, selepas melamar Khadeja, Ray bertemu bakal ibu mentuanya, Dato' Shikin, seorang ibu tunggal dan peguam terkenal. Tanpa mengetahui latar belakang keluarga Khadeja, Ray mendapati bahawa Dato' Shikin telah menyelidik kehidupan masa lalunya yang 'nakal. Demi mendapatkan restu bagi mengahwini Khadeja, Dato Shikin telah menetapkan satu syarat, Ray perlu berdepan dan meminta maaf kepada kesemua 11 bekas teman wanitanya, merakam setiap kemaafan yang diberikan kepada Ray, dan menghantarnya kepada Dato' Shikin dalam tempoh 30 hari. Terdesak, Ray bersetuju dengan syarat tersebut dan meminta bantuan rakan baiknya, Kamil. Misi menjadi rumit apabila Ray dan Kamil mendapati bekas-bekas teman wanitanya, pesakit mental, jurulatih MMA, pegawai polis narkotik, barista kafe, penjaga zoo, pengusaha makanan dan pelbagai lagi, kesemuanya masih marah dengan Ray, terutamanya Aisha, kenalan rapat Ray dari bangku sekolah yang juga kononnya salah seorang dari 11 orang bekas kekasih Ray. Kali terakhir Ray bertemu dengan Aisha adalah 13 tahun lepas. Aisha menyedari bahawa Ray benar-benar telah berubah dan memutuskan untuk membantu Ray menyelesaikan misinya. Ray dan Aisha secara tidak diduga mula jatuh hati antara satu sama lain. Perasaan yang sama dirasai mereka 13 tahun lepas namun dipendam sehingga kini. Tanpa pengetahuan Ray, Dato' Shikin telah mengupah seseorang yang rapat dengan Ray untuk menggagalkan misinya. Masa 30 hari kian hampir tamat, dan Aisha merupakan orang yang terakhir dalam misi Ray untuk memohon kemaafan

Siti Nor Aisya meninggalkan dunia glamournya demi Fareez namun tanpa dia duga.. Perkahwinan yg dibina tidak kekal lama. Rumahtangga dia dan Fareez diduga dengan kehadiran orang ketiga iaitu ADRIANA.

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep5
programme.desc: Lukman masih dihantui mimpi dan kenangan bersama arwah Sarah. Perasaan bersalah atas kematian Sarah tetap mengganggu minda dan emosinya. Dia sering terbayangkan arwah Sarah ketika bersama Farah. Perasaan kelirunya membuatkan Farah sering makan hati.

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep6
programme.desc: Zulkarnain pernah terkilan kerana familinya ada merancang untuk menjodohkannyadengan Farah, namun Farah pula dinikahi Lukman sebagai ganti tikar. Lukmanmempertikaikan tindakan Farah yang menghilangkan diri selama beberapa hari tanpamemberitahunya. Farah membidas Lukman yang culas amanah sebagai suami.

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep7
programme.desc: Farah terkejut apabila Lukman meninggikan suara hanya kerana dia memegang bajumilik arwah Sarah. Meskipun terkejut, namun Farah cuba memahami penderitaan dankecelaruan yang sedang ditanggung suaminya. Di tempat kerja, Farah didekati Anasyang sangat baik dengannya. Berbanding dengan Dahlia yang sering membulinyadi pejabat.

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep8
programme.desc: Farah panik apabila Zahin demam panas hingga muntah-muntah. KeadaanZahinmenyebabkan Farah dan Lukman dalam dilema untuk menyerahkan tugas menjagaZahin kerana masing-masing sedang sibuk. Farah mengalah dan terpaksa ambil cuti kecemasan meskipun dia baru bekerja. Kata-kata pedih daripada pengurusnya

programme.title: Huru Hara S15 Ep2

programme.title: 11 Cinta Sebelum Kamu
programme.desc: Ray, selepas melamar Khadeja, Ray bertemu bakal ibu mentuanya, Dato' Shikin, seorang ibu tunggal dan peguam terkenal. Tanpa mengetahui latar belakang keluarga Khadeja, Ray mendapati bahawa Dato' Shikin telah menyelidik kehidupan masa lalunya yang 'nakal. Demi mendapatkan restu bagi mengahwini Khadeja, Dato Shikin telah menetapkan satu syarat, Ray perlu berdepan dan meminta maaf kepada kesemua 11 bekas teman wanitanya, merakam setiap kemaafan yang diberikan kepada Ray, dan menghantarnya kepada Dato' Shikin dalam tempoh 30 hari. Terdesak, Ray bersetuju dengan syarat tersebut dan meminta bantuan rakan baiknya, Kamil. Misi menjadi rumit apabila Ray dan Kamil mendapati bekas-bekas teman wanitanya, pesakit mental, jurulatih MMA, pegawai polis narkotik, barista kafe, penjaga zoo, pengusaha makanan dan pelbagai lagi, kesemuanya masih marah dengan Ray, terutamanya Aisha, kenalan rapat Ray dari bangku sekolah yang juga kononnya salah seorang dari 11 orang bekas kekasih Ray. Kali terakhir Ray bertemu dengan Aisha adalah 13 tahun lepas. Aisha menyedari bahawa Ray benar-benar telah berubah dan memutuskan untuk membantu Ray menyelesaikan misinya. Ray dan Aisha secara tidak diduga mula jatuh hati antara satu sama lain. Perasaan yang sama dirasai mereka 13 tahun lepas namun dipendam sehingga kini. Tanpa pengetahuan Ray, Dato' Shikin telah mengupah seseorang yang rapat dengan Ray untuk menggagalkan misinya. Masa 30 hari kian hampir tamat, dan Aisha merupakan orang yang terakhir dalam misi Ray untuk memohon kemaafan

programme.title: Bawah Payung Awan Ep27
programme.desc: Widad dan Soleiman merancang untuk berkahwin setelah mendapat persetujuan Anita. Hanan yang marah apabila Dato AJ enggan menunaikan janjnya mengambil keputusan untuk menghapuskannya

programme.title: The Gadis Ep5
programme.desc: Mengisahkan ibu Shazman berjumpa dengan Lina, dia mahu Shazwan berkahwin dengan Nad dan bukan dengan Lina. Namun Nad sendiri pun tidak sukakan Shazman. Shazman datang, dia meminta maaf atas sikap ibunya. Shazman mendapat pekerjaan dan menjemput Lina dan keluarga ke rumahnya untuk majlis doa selamat. Lina meminta maaf atas perbuatannya sehingga membuat kakaknya marah. Lina minta Lisa tidak lagi berjumpa dengan Nad kerana merasakan pekerjaan yang dilakukan Nad sebagai pelaucr. Mulai saat itu Lisa merasa bersalah melihat kesungguhan kakaknya mencari wang halal untuk keluarga. Lisa nekad untuk berhenti menjadi sugar baby. Dia memberitahu Nad. Nad mengamuk. Dia perlukan Lisa untuk selesaikan hutangnya dengan Mika. Mika dan Nad bersekongkol untuk menculik Lisa ke KL agar mereka dapat selesaikan hal mereka. Di kampung, Lina risau Lisa tidak pulang-pulang. Lina pergi ke rumah Rocky dan mendapat tahu yang Lisa selama ini menipu. Lisa pengsan di rumah Nad selepas diberi dadah

programme.title: Epilog Yasmin
programme.desc: Telefilem Epilog Yasmin mengisahkan tentang Yasmin dan Nasir, pasangan yang sudah bertunang dan bakal berkahwin. Nasir merupakan seorang penulis dan sering berkongsi impiannya bersama Yasmin. Nasir sering menyatakan bahawa novel tulisanya akan menjadi sebuah novel "hot seller". Yasmin hanya ketawakan sahaja impian tunangnya itu kerana menganggap impian Nasir hanyalah sebuah angan-angan. Pada suatu hari, Nasir kemalangan dan meninggal dunia tanpa sempat menyiapkan novel karangannya. Selepas kematian Nasir, Yasmin berusaha menyiapkan novel tersebut demi sebuah cinta.

Pemanggil misteri itu memberitahu Aisya bahawa nyawa Malik dalam bahaya melainkan dia hadir di majlis tari-menari bertopeng itu. Berjayakah Black menangkap 419 akhirnya atau adakah pembunuh upahan itu dapat menghalang Black dan mengucar-ngacirkan misinya? programme.desc: Pesta Hantu Lapar sudah hampir. Seorang pekerja baru di telah menyinggung perasaan hantu di bangunan pejabatnya kerana dia tidak hormat kepada roh pada hari pertamanya bekerja. Semasa menjalani syif malam, lelaki itu dan rakan sekerjanya yang bekerja lebih masa mengalami pertemuan menyeramkan yang membuatkan mereka merenung tingkah laku dan kepercayaan mereka.

programme.desc: The show 'Top Singers' aims to spotlight outstanding Taiwanese singers and composers, setting a new standard in the industry. Combining elements of competition, variety, and personal stories, the show welcomes participants of all ages. Its goals include discovering grassroots talent, innovating Taiwanese song performance styles, and involving more local talent in song composition to infuse new life into Taiwanese music.

programme.title: Show Biz (M) Ep1014
programme.desc: Every second counts in "Show Biz" to bring you with the most High Speed star news, exciting live shows and performers interviews.

programme.title: Dear Mom (M) Ep46
programme.desc: Feng-Yi Li handles everything in the house while her husband, Shu-An, lounges and daydreams. She constantly worries about the love lives of their four daughters. Yi-Wan starts a relationship with a gang leaders son despite claiming to have never dated. Qing-Qing may be having an affair with a married man. Xiao-Xi is infatuated with the school team captain but is unaware of "the others." An-Qing returns from the US with her son after a failed marriage. When Feng-Yi suddenly disappears, the sisters realize they've neglected their mother, who has always supported them. Now they must find her and get their lives back on track.

programme.title: Protege
programme.desc: Undercover Police Nick has spent 8 years working for the drug baron Quin, so as to collect evidence of his drug trafficking activities. After gaining Quins trust, Nick becomes his protg and succeeds him as the drug baron when Quin retires. However, Nick has lost himself in his split life between trading drugs and searching for criminal evidence.

programme.title: PTU
programme.desc: When OCTB (Organized Crime And Triad Bureau) officer, Sergeant Lo Sa, loses his police revolver to four triad young thugs, he seeks help from Sergeant Mike Ho of the PTU (Police Tactical Unit) to find his lost revolver. Ho and his patrolling PTU team has until dawn to recover the gun and clean up the mess.

programme.title: The Invisible Guest
programme.desc: Young and beautiful entrepreneur Joanna is a prime suspect in a locked-room murder where her lover is found dead. She pays off a police officer to prove her innocence. During the investigation, they discover another murder case involving Joanna and her lover, and eventually reveals the truth.

programme.title: Echoes of the Rainbow
programme.desc: Set in Hong Kong in the 1960s, the story revolves around the family of a hardworking shoemaker Mr Law, with his happy-go-lucky wife and two sons a talented elder son and an eight-year-old eccentric younger son. While their lives are not always smooth-sailing, the family sticks together and support one another through thick and thin.

programme.title: The Ex-Files 4: Marriage Plan
programme.desc: Two brothers, Meng Yun and Yu Fei, are of marriageable age and are facing challenges in love. Yun dodges family pressure to marry after his breakup, while Fei and his girlfriend opt for a marriage cooling-off period to tackle marriage issues.

programme.title: Journey to the West: Conquering the Demons
programme.desc: The sequel to "Journey to the West: Conquering the Demons", this happens after Monkey King has gained enlightenment and is Tang San Zang's disciple. Tang, Monkey King, Sandy and Pigsy continue their journey to the West, where they have to fight and eliminate demons while dealing with their own changes, putting their bond to the test.

programme.title: Let It Ghost
programme.desc: The movie consists of three urban ghost stories: when a film crew is haunted by a ghost, the director decides to cast her to play the ghost; when a taxi driver takes his girlfriend to a staycation, a horny ghost adds spice to it; a wandering child ghost refuses to leave a mall that is to be demolished, so the tenants help her to move on.

programme.title: First Love the Litter on the Breeze
programme.desc: This movie is the directorial debut of actor Eric Kot for Wong Kar Wai. Eric features the topic of first love in his first movie: a sleepwalker guided through the night by a lonely admirer is bizarre yet romantic, while a married grocer facing the vengeful first love that he once rejected is heartbreaking.

programme.title: Young and Dangerous: Reloaded
programme.desc: In this remake of Young and Dangerous, Chan Ho Nam and his three buddies of the Hung Hing triad gang strive to fight for their own justice, further expanding their power in the triad and becoming a new legend...

programme.title: Raging Fire
programme.desc: As the police sets to arrest a drug lord, a team of masked thugs steals the drugs and murders the cops. Inspector Bong is devastated to see the aftermath of the carnage and soon discovers that the killers are led by Ngo, a former fellow cop who was forced into a life of crime by him. As the two men meet again, it is time to settle the score

programme.title: Ghost Wedding
programme.desc: Photographer Zhi Cheng is entangled with a "woman in red", leading to the deaths of his relatives one by one. When the girl he likes, Si Tong, also dies mysteriously, Zhi Cheng vows to find out the truth but ends up revealing the secret of a "ghost marriage"...

programme.title: Song of Spring
programme.desc: An 85-year-old mother lives with her 65-year-old daughter who is suffering from Alzheimer's disease, causing her to suffer a decline in memory, mental confusion and disorientation. Though the elderly mother has to shoulder the burden of a caregiver, she still wants to be with her daughter forever.

programme.title: Tristar
programme.desc: Young priest Hong disguises himself to protect Bai, a prostitute, while Detective Liu investigates her ties to a prostitution ring. Hong finds Bai a lawful job and helps her negotiate with the underworld. Meanwhile, Liu's investigation causes misunderstandings can he crack down on the gang? How will Hong manage his emotions as Bai falls for him?

programme.title: Journey to the West: Conquering the Demons
programme.desc: The sequel to "Journey to the West: Conquering the Demons", this happens after Monkey King has gained enlightenment and is Tang San Zang's disciple. Tang, Monkey King, Sandy and Pigsy continue their journey to the West, where they have to fight and eliminate demons while dealing with their own changes, putting their bond to the test.

programme.title: Love After Love
programme.desc: Directed by Ann Hui, the movie is adapted from Eileen Changs first short story. Set in 1930s, Wei Long travels to Hong Kong from Shanghai to pursue her education. Struggling financially, she asks her aunt to help pay for tuition but ends up being her aunts puppet to lure rich men. When Wei Long falls for playboy, George, she sinks into a life of depravity.

programme.title: Ashes of Time Redux
programme.desc: After his beloved woman married his brother, Ou Yang Feng moves to the desert to run an inn and becomes a killer agent. He makes acquaintance of different people with their different stories ... The movie is the winner of the 1st Hong Kong Film Critics Society Awards for Best Film, Best Director, Best Screenplay and Best Actor (Leslie Cheung).

programme.title: Love Punch
programme.desc: Talented boxer Jia Yang is caught in an underground fight to clear her father's debts. She loses her Olympic aspiration and vanishes from the boxing world. 10 years later, Coach Li Yue is determined to help her honour her father's wish by returning to the ring. As passion and obligation collide, can Jia Yang revive her abandoned boxing dream?

programme.title: Flirting Scholar from the Future
programme.desc: Tiger, Lambert and Skinny Pig are massive fans of the movie, Flirting Scholar. One day, Skinny Pig who is an obscure inventor, puts together a movie time machine and accidentally sucks all of them into the movie of Flirting Scholar. The trio head off to Wah mansion to meet the maid Autumn can they find her and can they return to the present?

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his familys expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his familys reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: Fagara
programme.desc: After her fathers death, a Hong Kong girl discovers she has two hitherto unknown sisters, Branch and Cherry. Through taking up her late fathers hotpot restaurant, she reunites with her sisters by different mothers, and understands her father more from a different perspective, allowing her to finally resolve her long-time hard feelings with him.

programme.title: Crypto Storm
programme.desc: ICAC investigation officer Lok sets up a special team to investigate a corruption case involving a banks top executives use of cryptocurrency to manipulate the trading market. When the banks chairman is kidnapped and kidnappers demand ransom in crypto coins, Lok connects the dots and vows to hunt down the mastermind behind both crimes.

programme.title: Soul Mate
programme.desc: July and An Sheng have been best friends since they were thirteen. They always believed their friendship would last forever, until they meet Su Jia Ming at the age of eighteen. The trio find themselves in a love triangle, which puts the girls friendship to the test and alters their destinies.

programme.title: Detective Dee and Nine-storey Demon Building
programme.desc: A series of strange incidents happen at the Tangs demon building but Detective Dee finds no clue. Dee finds the master of the family suspicious when he speaks with him, and when the eldest daughter Miss Tang secretly informs Dee about Mr Tangs strange behavior and the fact that she is kept under surveillance, Dee vows to unveil the truth.

programme.title: Over My Dead Body
programme.desc: This dark comedy begins with an unidentified corpse appearing at the doorstep of a residential flat. Fearing that the corpse will turn their flats into "haunted flats", which will cause a drastic drop in the property value, the four families living on the same floor attempt to move the corpse away, embroiling themselves in chaos.

programme.title: City Under Siege
programme.desc: When circus clown Sunny gets transformed into a super-powered mutant, he finds himself pitted against his fellow circus performers who were altered in the same accident, and who are now using their powers to wreak havoc around the city.

programme.title: Fatal Visit
programme.desc: Yanny leaves Hong Kong for San Jose to visit her old friend Ling. Ling and her husband Tang seems to live an ideal and carefree life. However, during her five-day stay, Yanny uncovers the truth behind the faade as she reveals the unspeakable secrets that will propel all three down a fatal path of destruction.

programme.title: Young Ip Man: Crisis Time
programme.desc: Set in 1917, young Ip Man pursues his studies in Hong Kong. The school is held hostage on the day of an English speech competition, and as Ip Man decides to step up and fight the crisis, it is revealed that his master and his childhood friend are behind all this. Can he take them down and uphold justice?

programme.title: Band Four
programme.desc: An aspiring singer of an indie band called Band Four reunites with her estranged guitarist father following the death of her mother. Together with her half-sister and her nine-year-old son, the newly reunited family come together to support each other through their love and passion for music.

programme.title: Mad Fate
programme.desc: A Master fortune teller predicts that Tung, a born psychopath, will be imprisoned for murder and tries to change his fate. A veteran detective believes Tung is a psychopathic serial killer after witnessing him kill a cat, and pursues him relentlessly. Can the Master change Tungs mad fate?

programme.title: Treasure Hunt
programme.desc: A commercial director Peggy shoots an ad on a deserted island while some mysterious men with the treasure map are also there to hunt for the hidden Ming Dynasty treasures. However, the map is stolen by Star who lives on the island. Star and Peggy unveil the hidden treasures but end up being chased by the mysterious men

programme.title: Bounty Hunters
programme.desc: A group of bounty hunters, including San, Yo, Cat, Swan and Bobo, are tasked to track down the culprit of a series of bombings that have plagued an international hotel group. Unfortunately, Swan, Cat and Bobo are kidnapped by the mastermind of the bombings. Can San and Yo save them? Will the bounty hunters accomplish their mission?

programme.title: Article 20
programme.desc: Han Ming, a prosecutor, faces a whirlwind of complications in his work and family lives: his son's clash with another student in school and his wife's intervention, as well as the strained partnerships at work. Amidst it all, a critical case challenges his sense of righteousness, and he decides to gamble everything to seek fairness and justice.

programme.title: Hong Kong Nocturne
programme.desc: This joyous, raucous, & colorful tunefest showcases the little seen dancing talents of celebrated kung-fu swordswoman Cheng Pei-Pei, as one of 3 girls dancing their way to the top.

programme.title: The Shaolin Avengers
programme.desc: Hu seeks to avenge his father who is being killed by the White-Browed Hermit and his gang. However, he fails in his attempt and is saved by Fang Shi Yu, a youth from Shaolin whose parents are also killed by the same villains. They learn and master the advanced Shaolin style kung fu, before Fang leads Hu and the Shaolin fellows to fight the enemies.

programme.title: The Bride from Hell
programme.desc: A young business man marries a pretty and much sought-after young bride, not knowing that she carries the spirit of a girl raped by her uncle and murdered along with her parents. Justice must be done, and it ain't pretty!

programme.title: The Magnificent Swordsman
programme.desc: The Magnificent Swordsman centres on the hero who vows vengeance against evil bandits who killed his family when he was a child. The hero recruits several friends to help the peasants rid their village of marauding bandits, the leader of the band being the man who killed his family.

programme.title: The Delinquent
programme.desc: This is a coming-of-age tale depicting the lower class Hong Kong troubled youths in the 1960s and the societal issues that they face. Wang Chung is a hotheaded and rebellious teen who is tempted by the dark side, and have to unfortunately pay a huge price for it.

programme.title: Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre
programme.desc: In the Yuan Dynasty, martial artists everywhere battle for the Heaven Sword and the Dragon Sabre, as only when these two powerful weapons combine can a secret be revealed to help one become the king of the martial arts world. As Zhang Wu Ji acquires the skills from Nine Yang Scriptures by chance, he is also embroiled in this lengthy battle.

programme.title: The Snake Prince
programme.desc: The Snake Prince lives on the Snake Mountain of Kwangsi with other snakes and they have lived peacefully with humans for a thousand years. All things change however, when the Snake Prince falls in love with one of the three beauties performing a sensual rain dance in the nearby village one day, and decides to marry her at all costs...

programme.title: The Love Eterne
programme.desc: Ying Tai disguises herself as a boy to go to school and falls hopelessly in love with her classmate, Shan Bo. After Shan Bo realizes her true identity, he proposes marriage to Ying Tai. However, they are kept apart as she is engaged to another man. Knowing Shan Bo died in despair, Ying Tai is in deep sorrow and kills herself at his grave.

programme.title: The Golden Seal
programme.desc: Dai Tian Chou practices martial arts since young so he can avenge his fathers death. He meets Wu Xiao Yan who is disguised as a man one day and is suddenly beaten by a group of gangsters. Wu begs her father to allow her to take Dai back home to recover. Little does Dai know this is his chance to take revenge.

programme.title: Invincible Enforcer
programme.desc: A young man is at the wrong place at the wrong time. As he offends a police inspector, he is thrown into jail and even when released, the police goes after him until he has no choice but to become a real criminal. Only a kind and beautiful probation officer is on his side, but can she help him?

programme.title: Forever Diamonds
programme.desc: Hua, a pretty fraud, steals a brilliant diamond ring from a shop in Hong Kong and escapes to Singapore. To smuggle the ring pass customs, Hua slips it into the pocket of a stranger, Yen, but then lost track of him. Hua finally spots Yen after searching for days and does everything to get close to him in order to take the ring back.

programme.title: The Scandalous Warlord
programme.desc: General Feng occupies the city of Shandong, and soldiers and civilians alike welcome him without knowing his tyrannical and lustful nature. His first official business is to inspect the brothels and take the prostitutes home to become his concubines. Feng is finally killed by his officers, but will the new general rule the city differently?

programme.title: The Kid with the Golden Arm
programme.desc: The government hires Yang to escort a cargo of gold to a famine stricken area. The vicious Chi Sha gang, with one of their best fighters, Golden Arm, announce their intention to hijack it by killing one of Yang's employees. As Yang gathers his own team of reputable fighters to protect his cargo, are they strong enough to hold off Golden Arm?

programme.title: Dead End
programme.desc: Uninhibited youth Chun meets a rich girl Wen when her car breaks down and drives her home. Chun falls in love with Wen but Wens brother dislikes him and forbids his sister to see him. He humiliates Chun and gets Chun beaten up, so Chun takes the pistol he has found accidentally on the street to Wens home and shoots her brother dead.

programme.title: Twin Blades Of Doom
programme.desc: A retired martial artist is forced to return with a vengeance after his family and friends are murdered by the evil Ghost Gang. He decides to challenge the gangs leader to a deadly duel so as to take revenge. Can he defeat the ruthless leader in the end?

programme.title: Apartment for Ladies
programme.desc: A Taiwanese singer comes to Hong Kong in search for her missing younger sister, who had arrived in Hong Kong to be discovered as a nightclub singer. She finds lodging at an apartment for women run by a man-hating landlady, Mrs Chan. However, Mrs Chan cannot confine the young ladies youthful vitality within the apartment.

programme.title: Dirty Ho
programme.desc: Master Wang, who is actually the 11th prince, poses as an antique connoisseur to hide his true identity. When he meets Dirty Ho, a witty con artist, Wang knows he has found the right man to help him untangle a royal succession plot...

programme.title: Pale Passion
programme.desc: Fa is an obsessive man who loves his wife Ah Hsia but is easily jealous and abuses her. When she leaves him one day, Fa hooks up with another woman, Hsing. A deadly triangle develops when Fa runs into Ah Hsia again and decides to win her back

programme.title: Heroes Shed No Tears
programme.desc: Kao Chien Fei is a young swordsman who wields a special sword with a teardrop marked on its blade. He is charged with averting an impending crisis in the martial arts world, but the villain, Zhou Tung Lai, wishes to become the ruler in the martial arts world, and launches a scheme to pit the various heroes against one another.

programme.title: Melody of Love
programme.desc: Three young doctors pursue three hard-to-get beauties in this romantic film set in the 70s a-go-go era. They have no idea where to start and use Rock-paper-scissor method to match themselves with the girls. The tactics and tricks they use are hilarious and they have to reshuffle their plans when nothing leads to success!

programme.title: The Silver Fox
programme.desc: The formidable swordswoman Silver Fox was a child when her father was senselessly wounded by his step brother, and her mother raped. It is payback time eighteen years later, as her father trains her up with kung fu to take revenge on his behalf.

programme.title: Sunset
programme.desc: Teenage heart-throbs Ching Li and Paul Chin Pei come across like Annette Funicello and Frankie Avalon in the musical Sunset, a musical romp that plays similar to one of Hollywood's famous "Beach Party" movies. A car load of girls meets a car load of boys, and Ching and Paul ultimately fall in love. Yet the film takes an acrid twist and turns out to be more like a Shakespearian tragedy than a beach-babe party.

programme.title: Murder Plot
programme.desc: Martial artist Shen Lang is in discussions with kung fu experts from the other six sects to plot the downfall of the traitorous Happy King when his fiance suddenly disrupts them and Shen has to quickly bring her away. As they continue to pursue the Happy King, both Shen and his fiance accidentally fall into a trap set up by the King.

programme.title: Scandal
programme.desc: The roguish scamp Zhen and his best friend Chia collects proof of corruption from the officials in this comedy-drama. After a string of blackmailing, they end up in positions of power, but what is to happen next?

programme.title: The Eunuch
programme.desc: A year before Lo Wei directed Bruce Lee in Fist Of Fury, he wrote and co-starred in this tale of a treacherous devil who wants nothing less than supreme power...and doesn't care if he has to murder the Emperor and use his own daughter as a deadly dupe to get it.

programme.title: Judgement of an Assassin
programme.desc: An evil clan plans a discord so as to dominate the martial arts world. Their masked assassins massacre another clan and one of the assassins is arrested and brought to trial at a tribunal of all the clans. What judgement will they make and can they uncover the truth?

programme.title: Shaolin Prince
programme.desc: As the names of Chang Cheh and Liu Chia-liang became legendary, all-too-often the name of their equally valued collaborator, Tang Chia, is omitted. That may be, because, unlike the previous pair, the veteran kung-fu choreographer only went on to direct three movies of his own. Of course, that makes this trio all the more special, and this first effort perhaps the most special of all. It may be an eye-filling, mind-bending martial arts tale of two royal princes battling for the rightful recovery of the throne, but it's also a party, where Tang invites two cinematographers, three editors, and no less than five other choreographer friends to almost literally shoot the works. The results are kung-fu configurations not only never seen before, but never even imagined!

programme.title: The Boxer From The Temple
programme.desc: A young monk, The Kid, was expelled from the temple due to his crazy ways. After leaving the temple, he fights a cruel bandit's son and befriends a prostitute. As he fights for justice, his Crazy Lo Han Fist improves with every fight.

programme.title: The Adventures of Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung travels incognito to Jiangnan to review his peoples livelihood but soon discovers that corrupt officials are oppressing his people. The emperor meets an upright young man and they join hands to teach the corrupt officials a lesson. The young man was appointed as his bodyguard thereafter.

programme.title: The Thundering Sword
programme.desc: Two disciples, Yu and Zheng, are sent by their master to track down the invincible weapon Thundering Sword to prevent villains from getting it. Yu encounters the daughter of a ruthless clan, Chiao, who is on her way to seek for the sword. They quickly fall for each other, but when Chiao accidentally injures Zheng, things become complicated.

programme.title: The Dancing Millionairess
programme.desc: Peter was a key dancer in a dance troupe and applied to be the chauffeur of a rich girl, Betty. When he is rumoured to be her lover, Betty is furious and goes undercover as a reporter to investigate the rumour. They fall in love in the process, and after putting Peter through many tests, they finally seal their love with a dance.

programme.title: Pursuit
programme.desc: This movie tells the tale of Lin Chong, the Sung Dynastys Chief Army Instructor who is framed by a corrupt official and has to embark on an exile fraught with danger. Helped by a monk, Lin Chong is finally able to take revenge.

programme.title: Forever And Ever
programme.desc: Ivy Ling Po plays a young scholar who is manipulated into marrying a nobleman's reluctant daughter. After marrying, he soon discovers the reason for her hesitation. She is stricken with a contagious disease. But, with the power of true love, their romance prevails.

programme.title: Perils Of The Sentimental Swordsman
programme.desc: The titanic team of Director Chu Yuan and Novelist Ku Lung chose to give their hero (Ti Lung) a whole new cliffhanger-fraught adventure featuring a mysterious swordsman, a sensual swordswoman, an imperial assassin, a ghost mansion, a booby-trapped tunnel, as well as double crosses and secret missions.

programme.title: The Perfumed Arrow
programme.desc: A charming Huangmei Opera title, this is the story of Fei E, a Generals daughter who grows up fooling everyone that she is a boy, including her two closest schoolmates. When she has to choose one of them to marry, how will Fei E tell them that she is a girl? To complicate matters, a girl who Fei E saves one day only wants to be married to her!

programme.title: Dragon Swamp
programme.desc: Fan is cheated by her lover Tong to steal her masters Jade Dragon Sword. She is jailed in the Dragon Swamp as punishment and gave birth to a pair of twins - her daughter is raised by her master, while her son is taken by Tong. Twenty years later, the sword is stolen again and Fans daughter goes seeking for it, meeting Fans friend along the way.
